---
title: Mushroom Flatbreads with Gouda Cream Sauce & Parmesan
description: Yes we love our simple cheese pizza with red sauce but tonight, move over, marinara—there’s a new sauce in town. In this recipe, crispy flatbreads are slathered with a rich, creamy gouda-mustard sauce we just can’t get enough of. We top that off with a pile of caramelized onion and earthy cremini mushrooms. Shower with Parmesan, and that’s it. Simple, satisfying, and all in 30 minutes–a dinner idea you can’t pass up!
